<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462310/extras/031d097080c6798e50abadcc7d3dea3a.poster.avif?t=1689744672\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462310/extras/031d097080c6798e50abadcc7d3dea3a.webm?t=1689744672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462310/extras/031d097080c6798e50abadcc7d3dea3a.mp4?t=1689744672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>                          you<br><br><br><br><strong>If you've accumulated some money, spinning the gacha can be fun!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462310/extras/f9d81910942c95a640cb08677ee8b9ca.poster.avif?t=1689744672\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462310/extras/f9d81910942c95a640cb08677ee8b9ca.webm?t=1689744672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462310/extras/f9d81910942c95a640cb08677ee8b9ca.mp4?t=1689744672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><strong>Opening the Pandora's box triggers a fever time!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462310/extras/f63f31443dae3cd33b6de87e361035ba.poster.avif?t=1689744672\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462310/extras/f63f31443dae3cd33b6de87e361035ba.webm?t=1689744672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462310/extras/f6